[DhtmlXQ_open]E23 仙人指路转左中炮对卒底炮飞左象[/DhtmlXQ_open]
[DhtmlXQ_remark]徐天利[/DhtmlXQ_remark]
[DhtmlXQ_author]许以劲[/DhtmlXQ_author]
